node.title: Man in critical condition after stabbing in Auckland
node.description: A man is in a critical condition in hospital after a stabbing in Auckland.
node.content: ["A man is in a critical condition in hospital after a stabbing in Auckland.", "Police were called to reports of a fight between a large group of people on Beach Road at around 2.30am today.", "The man is now having emergency surgery.", "Two other people were injured and are in a stable condition in hospital.", "Police are reviewing CCTV footage as part of their investigation."]
